									<p><img src="images/3698-45648-saf_2015_hero.jpg" alt="3698-45648-saf_2015_hero" title="3698-45648-saf_2015_hero" data-linktype="relative-path"/> </p>
<h1 id="thank-you-for-joining-us-at-microsofts-strategic-architect-forum-2015">Thank you for joining us at Microsoft’s Strategic Architect Forum 2015</h1>
<h3 id="session-videos-and-presentations-are-now-available-online">Session videos and presentations are now available online</h3>
<p>See sessions, presentations and additional relevant content here</p>
<p>Architecture blueprintsScenario-based diagrams that help you build new solutions fast<img src="images/3575-36050-overview-cta-1.jpg" alt="Watch the architecture video" title="3575-36050-overview-cta-1.jpg" data-linktype="relative-path"/>Watch the videoTransform technology to an asset to grow your business and your career&lt;iframe width=&quot;980&quot; height=&quot;550&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;true&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; marginwidth=&quot;0&quot; marginheight='0' scrolling=&quot;no&quot; src=&quot;https://hubs-video.ssl.catalog.video.msn.com/embed/e64ef54d-5b87-4d59-b780-42d21ddf02d9/?%3D&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;EasyJet: Leading European airline improves service and scalabilityMYOB: Business software firm gives customers online/offline cloud accessDell: Uses cloud solution to manage online traffic, customer dealsGo to case studies<img src="images/3702-win12_vipul_07.png" alt="" title="3702-win12_vipul_07.png" data-linktype="relative-path"/>Read moreDiscover articles, whitepapers and more and learn about top trending architecture topics.<img src="images/3578-36050-overview-cta-3.jpg" alt="Architects blog" title="3578-36050-overview-cta-3.jpg" data-linktype="relative-path"/>Go to blogMicrosoft blogs about all things for enterprise architects.</p>

